  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.8.6">
<l>kalanteṉ ṉāvi</l>
<l>nalaṅko ṇātaṉ</l>
<l>pulaṉkoṇ māṇāy</l>
<l>nilaṅkoṇ ṭāṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As he mingled with my soul,</l>
<l>the lord who took my goodness,</l>
<l>as a boy who captures the senses</l>
<l>he took the earth.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
